      "originalText": "Same Distance → S ∝ 1/T (inverse)\n  S1/S2 = T2/T1\n  Double speed = Half time\n\nSame Time → S ∝ D (direct)\n  Double speed = Double distance\n\nSame Speed → D ∝ T (direct)",
