      "x": 65,
      "y": 372,
      "width": 242,
      "height": 110,
      "text": "Same dir (chase/overtake):\n  ──→  ──→  Rel = S1 - S2\n\nOpposite dir (meeting):\n  ──→  ←──  Rel = S1 + S2\n\nCatch-up time = Gap / Rel speed",
