    {
      "id": "el_17",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 372,
      "width": 336,
      "height": 172,
      "text": "Late/Early → find distance:\n  D = S1 × S2 × T / (S2 - S1)\n\n  T = time difference:\n  Late+Early → T = late + early\n  Both late  → T = late1 - late2\n  Convert minutes to hours first!\n\n  Ex: 40km/h→10min late, 60km/h→10min early\n  T = 10+10 = 20min = 1/3 hr\n  D = 40×60×(1/3) / (60-40) = 40 km",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 1700,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 17,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f4"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Late/Early → find distance:\n  D = S1 × S2 × T / (S2 - S1)\n\n  T = time difference:\n  Late+Early → T = late + early\n  Both late  → T = late1 - late2\n  Convert minutes to hours first!\n\n  Ex: 40km/h→10min late, 60km/h→10min early\n  T = 10+10 = 20min = 1/3 hr\n  D = 40×60×(1/3) / (60-40) = 40 km",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
