        "type_1"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Distance=240 km, Time=4 hrs\nStep 2: Speed = Distance/Time = 240/4 = 60\n\nTRICK (D-S-T triangle):\n  D=S×T → S=D/T → T=D/S\n\n  A ════════ 240 km ════════ B\n  ──────────────────────────→\n              4 hours\n\n  S = 240/4 = 60 km/h\n\nAnswer: 60 km/h ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
