    },
    {
      "id": "el_38",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 1101,
      "width": 245,
      "height": 216,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: D1=40×2=80, D2=60×2=120\n  Total=200km, Total time=4hrs\nStep 2: Avg = 200/4 = 50 km/h\n\nTRICK (same time → simple avg):\nAvg = (S1+S2)/2 = (40+60)/2 = 50\n\n  |◄── 2 hrs ──►|◄── 2 hrs ──►|\n  |  40 km/h     |  60 km/h     |\n  |  80 km       |  120 km      |\n\nSame time = arithmetic mean works!\n\nAnswer: 50 km/h ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 3800,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 38,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_4"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: D1=40×2=80, D2=60×2=120\n  Total=200km, Total time=4hrs\nStep 2: Avg = 200/4 = 50 km/h\n\nTRICK (same time → simple avg):\nAvg = (S1+S2)/2 = (40+60)/2 = 50\n\n  |◄── 2 hrs ──►|◄── 2 hrs ──►|\n  |  40 km/h     |  60 km/h     |\n  |  80 km       |  120 km      |\n\nSame time = arithmetic mean works!\n\nAnswer: 50 km/h ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
