      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_5"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: T1=120/40=3h, T2=180/60=3h\nStep 2: Total D=300, Total T=6\n  Avg = 300/6 = 50 km/h\n\nTRICK (check if shortcut applies):\nDiff dist + diff time → NO formula shortcut\nMust use: Avg = Total D / Total T\n\n  |◄─ 120 km ─►|◄── 180 km ──►|\n  |   40 km/h   |   60 km/h    |\n\nHere T1=T2=3h (coincidence!) → 300/6=50\n\nAnswer: 50 km/h ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
