    {
      "id": "el_53",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 1501,
      "width": 296,
      "height": 202,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: D=S×T. Same T → D directly ∝ S\n  S=5:7 → D=5:7\nStep 2: If one=150: 5 parts=150→1 part=30\n  Other = 7×30 = 210 km\n\nTRICK (proportionality):\nSame time → Dist ratio = Speed ratio\nSame dist → Time ratio = inverse Speed\nSame speed → Dist ratio = Time ratio\n\nHere: S=5:7, same T → D=5:7\n\nAnswer: Distance ratio = 5:7 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 5300,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 53,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_7"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: D=S×T. Same T → D directly ∝ S\n  S=5:7 → D=5:7\nStep 2: If one=150: 5 parts=150→1 part=30\n  Other = 7×30 = 210 km\n\nTRICK (proportionality):\nSame time → Dist ratio = Speed ratio\nSame dist → Time ratio = inverse Speed\nSame speed → Dist ratio = Time ratio\n\nHere: S=5:7, same T → D=5:7\n\nAnswer: Distance ratio = 5:7 ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
