    {
      "id": "el_63",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 1501,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 202,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Opposite → Rel=30+50=80 km/h\n  Meet in = 120/80 = 1.5 hrs\nStep 2: From X: 30×1.5 = 45 km\n\nTRICK (ratio shortcut):\nA:B = 30:50 = 3:5\nDist from X = (3/8)×120 = 45 km\n\n  X ═══════ 120 km ═══════ Y\n  A──→ 30              50 ←──B\n       meet at 45km from X\n\nAnswer: Meet at 45 km from X ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
