      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Opposite → Rel=30+50=80 km/h\n  Meet in = 120/80 = 1.5 hrs\nStep 2: From X: 30×1.5 = 45 km\n\nTRICK (ratio shortcut):\nA:B = 30:50 = 3:5\nDist from X = (3/8)×120 = 45 km\n\n  X ═══════ 120 km ═══════ Y\n  A──→ 30              50 ←──B\n       meet at 45km from X\n\nAnswer: Meet at 45 km from X ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
