    {
      "id": "el_73",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 1898,
      "width": 303,
      "height": 188,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: B has 2 km head start\n  Same dir → Rel = 10-8 = 2 km/h\nStep 2: Time = Gap/Rel = 2/2 = 1 hr\n\nTRICK (catch-up formula):\nTime = Head start dist / (S_fast - S_slow)\n= 2/(10-8) = 1 hr\n\n  B──→8          A──→10\n     |◄── 2 km ──►|\n\nAnswer: 1 hr ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
