    {
      "id": "el_78",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 1914,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 173,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: D/6 + D/10 = 4 hours\n  (5D+3D)/30 = 4 → 8D = 120 → D = 15\n\nTRICK (avg speed shortcut):\nAvg = 2×6×10/(6+10) = 120/16 = 7.5\nTotal dist = 7.5×4 = 30 → D = 15 km\n\n  A ═══ D km ═══ B\n    ──→ 6 km/h  ←── 10 km/h\n\nAnswer: 15 km ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 7800,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 78,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_12"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: D/6 + D/10 = 4 hours\n  (5D+3D)/30 = 4 → 8D = 120 → D = 15\n\nTRICK (avg speed shortcut):\nAvg = 2×6×10/(6+10) = 120/16 = 7.5\nTotal dist = 7.5×4 = 30 → D = 15 km\n\n  A ═══ D km ═══ B\n    ──→ 6 km/h  ←── 10 km/h\n\nAnswer: 15 km ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
