    },
    {
      "id": "el_98",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 2725,
      "width": 317,
      "height": 216,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Let D=total. Each part=D/3\n  T = D/(3×20)+D/(3×30)+D/(3×60)\n  = D/60+D/90+D/180 = (3D+2D+D)/180 = 6D/180\nStep 2: Avg = D/(6D/180) = 180/6 = 30\n\nTRICK (equal parts formula):\nAvg = 3/(1/S1+1/S2+1/S3)\n= 3/(1/20+1/30+1/60)\n= 3/(6/60) = 3/(1/10) = 30\n\n  |◄─D/3─►|◄─D/3─►|◄─D/3─►|\n  | 20km/h | 30km/h | 60km/h |\n\nAnswer: 30 km/h ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 9800,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 98,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_16"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Let D=total. Each part=D/3\n  T = D/(3×20)+D/(3×30)+D/(3×60)\n  = D/60+D/90+D/180 = (3D+2D+D)/180 = 6D/180\nStep 2: Avg = D/(6D/180) = 180/6 = 30\n\nTRICK (equal parts formula):\nAvg = 3/(1/S1+1/S2+1/S3)\n= 3/(1/20+1/30+1/60)\n= 3/(6/60) = 3/(1/10) = 30\n\n  |◄─D/3─►|◄─D/3─►|◄─D/3─►|\n  | 20km/h | 30km/h | 60km/h |\n\nAnswer: 30 km/h ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
